Second Department,

June, 1956

(June 1, 1956) In the Matter of Edward H. Freiberger, Appellant, against Donald L. O’Toole et al., Respondents.

Order on reargument affirmed, without costs. Appeal from original orders dismissed, without costs. No opinion. Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldock, Murphy and Kleinfeld, JJ., concur. [2 Misc 2d 191.]
